Description_lang: Increases the damage done by your Corruption spell by $s1%, increases the damage done by your Incinerate spell by $s2%, and increases the damage done by your Shadow Bolt, Touch of Chaos, and Demonic Slash by $s3%.

description_blz.en_US: Increases the damage done by your Corruption spell by 10%, increases the damage done by your Incinerate spell by 5%, and increases the damage done by your Shadow Bolt, Touch of Chaos, and Demonic Slash by 2%.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta el daño infligido por tu hechizo Corrupción un 10%, aumenta el daño infligido por tu hechizo Incinerar un 5% y aumenta el daño infligido por tu Descarga de las Sombras, Toque de Caos y Tajo demoníaco un 2%.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aumenta em 10% o dano causado pelo seu feitiço Corrupção, aumenta em 5% o dano causado pelo feitiço Incinerar e aumenta em 2% o dano causado pelos seus feitiços Seta Sombria, Toque do Caos e Talho Demoníaco.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht den von Eurem Zauber 'Verderbnis' verursachten Schaden um 10%, erhöht den von Eurem Zauber 'Verbrennen' verursachten Schaden um 5% und erhöht den von Eurem Zauber 'Schattenblitz' und Euren Fähigkeiten 'Dämonischer Hieb' und 'Berührung des Chaos' verursachten Schaden um 2%.
description_blz.en_GB: Increases the damage done by your Corruption spell by 10%, increases the damage done by your Incinerate spell by 5%, and increases the damage done by your Shadow Bolt, Touch of Chaos, and Demonic Slash by 2%.
description_blz.es_ES: Aumenta el daño infligido por tu hechizo Corrupción un 10%, aumenta el daño infligido por tu hechizo Incinerar un 5% y aumenta el daño infligido por tu Descarga de las Sombras, Toque de Caos y Tajo demoníaco un 2%.
description_blz.fr_FR: Augmente les dégâts infligés par votre sort Corruption de 10%, augmente les dégâts infligés par votre sort Incinérer de 5%, et augmente les dégâts infligés par vos sorts Trait de l’ombre et Lame de chaos ainsi que votre technique Entaille démoniaque de 2%.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta i danni inflitti da Corruzione del 10%, i danni inflitti da Incenerimento del 5% e i danni inflitti da Dardo d'Ombra, Tocco del Caos e Fendente Demoniaco del 2%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Увеличивает урон, наносимый "Порчей", на 10%, "Испепелением" – на 5%, "Стрелой Тьмы", "Касанием Хаоса" и "Кнутом демона" – на 2%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 부패 주문의 공격력이 10%만큼, 소각 주문의 공격력이 5%만큼, 어둠의 화살, 혼돈의 손길, 악마의 베기의 공격력이 2%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 使你腐蝕術造成的傷害提高10%，燒盡造成的傷害提高5%，暗影箭、混沌之觸與惡魔斬擊造成的傷害提高2%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 你的腐蚀术造成的伤害提高10%，烧尽造成的伤害提高5%，且暗影箭、混乱之触和恶魔猛击造成的伤害提高2%。
